            <title><![CDATA[Sales 2020 : Regis Lemmens at TEDxLiege]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<article><h1>Sales 2020 : Regis Lemmens at TEDxLiege</h1><p>Unlike a sales approach that  treats customers as targets and which is based on persuasion and promises, co-creation is based on partnering with customers and collaborate with them to deliver real value. Make customer buy from you and stop selling to them.</p><img src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/the-grid-img/p/768102dcdfdef7c5d893e8d89f6d9f3b82a515c3.jpg"></article>]]></description>
